summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 221W, Page 7 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Block 3, Brockman's Tracts Unrecorded from RS 7200 to RM 800, and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (C.F. 284152 Petition of George W. Shellhorn).
